title: S13 Ep112: Supernatural News/Parashare: Episode 179
itunes:title: Supernatural News/Parashare: Episode 179
description: BEYOND the DARKNESS is back to report Supernatural News from around the world and share YOUR Paranormal phone calls! plus, while Dave is away this week, Tim has recruited the one and only, Mallie Fox to fill in!  It's a strange week of stories with President Trump having visitors from beyond playing through his golf course, The Hunt for the Skinwalker is coming to the big screen, and a square object in the sky nearly scares a man to death! PLUS we answer your calls in our ParaShare segment.
